      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LITTLE MASTER (1) is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 6th in a Grade 5 on February 20 over 300m at this track behind Chasing Sunset beaten 2.5 lengths (17.02). With a clean break looks hard to beat. DUNSMORE FLYER (5) hit the ground running from an outside draw with a fast early split, paving the way for a 0.8 lengths win at this track over 300m in 17.16. Capable of going well again. LETHAL TRIX (4) turned in a fair run last time from an unfavourable draw finishing fourth by 1.1 lengths (16.93). Solid record here at the distance winning three races. Has ability and is one of the better chances. PUNCH DRUNK LOVE (2) is a last-start placegetter who should be thereabouts.",
